title: Robbie Swifthand and the Orb of Mysteries-TiNYiSO
description:

Robbie Swifthand and the Orb of Mysteries
(c) Pixel Reign

Release On: 21 September 2018 Disk Amount/Format: 1 Disc
Type of Game: Action Media Protection: Steam

Robbie Swifthand and the Orb of Mysteries! A hardcore 2D platformer that
will "mess with your mind" and test your skills. Enter a Temple full
of devious traps and of course, lots of treasure!

NOTE:

To our friends from the Amiga days - if you liked Rick Dangerous, this
game will please the hell out of you :-)

Burn/mount, install, copy crack, play!
